title: Iced Banana Bomb By VGOD
description: Dry Tobacco by VGOD SaltNic E-Liquid delivers a decadent tobacco flavor that has a pleasing, mild sweetness. Not all users enjoy the fruity, dessert or menthol flavored e-juices in their pod systems.
